#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.54"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.54:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: 6. Abyākatavagga → abyākatavatthusuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.54:0.2"
msgid "6. Abyākatavagga "
msgstr "6. The Undeclared Points "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 54. Abyākatasutta → paṇṇāsakāsaṅgahitā vaggā (s1, s2) | paṇṇāsakasaṅgahitā vaggā (s3)
msgctxt "an7.54:0.3"
msgid "54. Abyākatasutta "
msgstr "54. The Undeclared Points "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.68, sc1
msgctxt "an7.54:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.54:1.2"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu ko paccayo yena sutavato ariyasāvakassa vicikicchā nuppajjati abyākatavatthūsū”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why an educated noble disciple has no doubts regarding the undeclared points?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an7.54:2.1"
msgid "“Diṭṭhinirodhā kho, bhikkhu, sutavato ariyasāvakassa vicikicchā nuppajjati abyākatavatthūsu. "
msgstr "“Mendicant, it’s due to the cessation of views that an educated noble disciple has no doubts regarding the undeclared points. "

msgctxt "an7.54:2.2"
msgid "‘Hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti kho, bhikkhu, diṭṭhigatametaṃ; "
msgstr "‘A Realized One exists after death’: this is a misconception. "

msgctxt "an7.54:2.3"
msgid "‘na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti kho, bhikkhu, diṭṭhigatametaṃ; "
msgstr "‘A Realized One doesn’t exist after death’: this is a misconception. "

msgctxt "an7.54:2.4"
msgid "‘hoti ca na ca hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti kho, bhikkhu, diṭṭhigatametaṃ; "
msgstr "‘A Realized One both exists and doesn’t exist after death’: this is a misconception. "

msgctxt "an7.54:2.5"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti kho, bhikkhu, diṭṭhigatametaṃ. "
msgstr "‘A Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death’: this is a misconception. "

msgctxt "an7.54:2.6"
msgid "Assutavā, bhikkhu, puthujjano diṭṭhiṃ nappajānāti, diṭṭhisamudayaṃ nappajānāti, diṭṭhinirodhaṃ nappajānāti, diṭṭhinirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ nappajānāti. "
msgstr "An uneducated ordinary person doesn’t understand views, their origin, their cessation, or the practice that leads to their cessation. "

msgctxt "an7.54:2.7"
msgid "Tassa sā diṭṭhi pavaḍḍhati, so na parimuccati jātiyā jarāya maraṇena sokehi paridevehi dukkhehi domanassehi upāyāsehi, na parimuccati dukkhasmāti vadāmi. "
msgstr "And so their views grow. They’re not freed from rebirth, old age, and death, from sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress. They’re not freed from suffering, I say. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an7.54:3.1"
msgid "Sutavā ca kho, bhikkhu, ariyasāvako diṭṭhiṃ pajānāti, diṭṭhisamudayaṃ pajānāti, diṭṭhinirodhaṃ pajānāti, diṭṭhinirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "An educated noble disciple does understand views, their origin, their cessation, and the practice that leads to their cessation. "

msgctxt "an7.54:3.2"
msgid "Tassa sā diṭṭhi nirujjhati, so parimuccati jātiyā jarāya maraṇena sokehi paridevehi dukkhehi domanassehi upāyāsehi, parimuccati dukkhasmāti vadāmi. "
msgstr "And so their views cease. They’re freed from rebirth, old age, and death, from sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress. They’re freed from suffering, I say. "

msgctxt "an7.54:3.3"
msgid "Evaṃ jānaṃ kho, bhikkhu, sutavā ariyasāvako evaṃ passaṃ ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipi na byākaroti; "
msgstr "Knowing and seeing this, an educated noble disciple does not answer: ‘A Realized One exists after death’, "

msgctxt "an7.54:3.4"
msgid "‘na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipi na byākaroti; "
msgstr "‘a Realized One doesn’t exist after death’, "

msgctxt "an7.54:3.5"
msgid "‘hoti ca na ca hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipi na byākaroti; "
msgstr "‘a Realized One both exists and doesn’t exist after death’, "

msgctxt "an7.54:3.6"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipi na byākaroti. "
msgstr "‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death.’ "

msgctxt "an7.54:3.7"
msgid "Evaṃ jānaṃ kho, bhikkhu, sutavā ariyasāvako evaṃ passaṃ evaṃ abyākaraṇadhammo hoti abyākatavatthūsu. "
msgstr "Knowing and seeing this, an educated noble disciple does not declare the undeclared points. "

msgctxt "an7.54:3.8"
msgid "Evaṃ jānaṃ kho, bhikkhu, sutavā ariyasāvako evaṃ passaṃ na chambhati, na kampati, na vedhati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati abyākatavatthūsu. "
msgstr "Knowing and seeing this, an educated noble disciple doesn’t shake, tremble, quake, or become nervous regarding the undeclared points. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.69, sc4
msgctxt "an7.54:4.1"
msgid "‘Hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti kho, bhikkhu, taṇhāgatametaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "‘A Realized One exists after death’: this is just about craving. … "

msgctxt "an7.54:4.2"
msgid "saññāgatametaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "it’s just about perception … "

msgctxt "an7.54:4.3"
msgid "maññitametaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "it’s an identification … "

msgctxt "an7.54:4.4"
msgid "papañcitametaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "it’s a proliferation … "

msgctxt "an7.54:4.5"
msgid "upādānagatametaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "it’s just about grasping … "

msgctxt "an7.54:4.6"
msgid "‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti kho, bhikkhu, vippaṭisāro eso; "
msgstr "‘A Realized One exists after death’: this is a regret. "

msgctxt "an7.54:4.7"
msgid "‘na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti kho, bhikkhu, vippaṭisāro eso; "
msgstr "‘A Realized One doesn’t exist after death’: this is a regret. "

msgctxt "an7.54:4.8"
msgid "‘hoti ca na ca hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti kho, bhikkhu, vippaṭisāro eso; "
msgstr "‘A Realized One both exists and doesn’t exist after death’: this is a regret. "

msgctxt "an7.54:4.9"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti kho, bhikkhu, vippaṭisāro eso. "
msgstr "‘A Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death’: this is a regret. "

msgctxt "an7.54:4.10"
msgid "Assutavā, bhikkhu, puthujjano vippaṭisāraṃ nappajānāti, vippaṭisārasamudayaṃ nappajānāti, vippaṭisāranirodhaṃ nappajānāti, vippaṭisāranirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ nappajānāti. "
msgstr "An uneducated ordinary person doesn’t understand regrets, their origin, their cessation, or the practice that leads to their cessation. "

msgctxt "an7.54:4.11"
msgid "Tassa so vippaṭisāro pavaḍḍhati, so na parimuccati jātiyā jarāya maraṇena sokehi paridevehi dukkhehi domanassehi upāyāsehi, na parimuccati dukkhasmāti vadāmi. "
msgstr "And so their regrets grow. They’re not freed from rebirth, old age, and death, from sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress. They’re not freed from suffering, I say. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.70, sc5
msgctxt "an7.54:5.1"
msgid "Sutavā ca kho, bhikkhu, ariyasāvako vippaṭisāraṃ pajānāti, vippaṭisārasamudayaṃ pajānāti, vippaṭisāranirodhaṃ pajānāti, vippaṭisāranirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "An educated noble disciple does understand regrets, their origin, their cessation, and the practice that leads to their cessation. "

msgctxt "an7.54:5.2"
msgid "Tassa so vippaṭisāro nirujjhati, so parimuccati jātiyā … pe … dukkhasmāti vadāmi. "
msgstr "And so their regrets cease. They’re freed from rebirth, old age, and death, from sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress. They’re freed from suffering, I say. "

msgctxt "an7.54:5.3"
msgid "Evaṃ jānaṃ kho, bhikkhu, sutavā ariyasāvako evaṃ passaṃ ‘hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipi na byākaroti … pe … "
msgstr "Knowing and seeing this, an educated noble disciple does not answer: ‘A Realized One exists after death’ … "

msgctxt "an7.54:5.4"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipi na byākaroti. "
msgstr "‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after death.’ "

msgctxt "an7.54:5.5"
msgid "Evaṃ jānaṃ kho, bhikkhu, sutavā ariyasāvako evaṃ passaṃ evaṃ abyākaraṇadhammo hoti abyākatavatthūsu. "
msgstr "Knowing and seeing this, an educated noble disciple does not declare the undeclared points. "

msgctxt "an7.54:5.6"
msgid "Evaṃ jānaṃ kho, bhikkhu, sutavā ariyasāvako evaṃ passaṃ na chambhati, na kampati, na vedhati, na santāsaṃ āpajjati abyākatavatthūsu. "
msgstr "Knowing and seeing this, an educated noble disciple doesn’t shake, tremble, quake, or become nervous regarding the undeclared points. "

msgctxt "an7.54:5.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhu, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yena sutavato ariyasāvakassa vicikicchā nuppajjati abyākatavatthūsū”ti. "
msgstr "This is the cause, this is the reason why an educated noble disciple has no doubts regarding the undeclared points.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.54:5.8"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

